00:00:04.470 --> 00:00:06.010
- Good afternoon, everyone.

00:00:06.010 --> 00:00:06.619
I'm Liz Cohen.

00:00:06.619 --> 00:00:08.910
I'm Dean of the Radcliffe
Institute for Advanced Study,

00:00:08.910 --> 00:00:12.990
and I am so pleased to welcome
you to this year's Julia S.

00:00:12.990 --> 00:00:16.290
Phelps Lecture in the
Arts and Humanities.

00:00:16.290 --> 00:00:19.110
Here at Radcliffe, we
have a twofold mission--

00:00:19.110 --> 00:00:23.700
to support pathbreaking research
and creative endeavors across

00:00:23.700 --> 00:00:27.480
