00:00:31.470 --> 00:00:34.290
Today, we are gathered for
the annual Phelps lecture

00:00:34.290 --> 00:00:37.020
in honor of Julia S. Phelps.

00:00:37.020 --> 00:00:39.660
Julia was a Radcliffe
College graduate

00:00:39.660 --> 00:00:42.630
who worked as an art
historian, a curator,

00:00:42.630 --> 00:00:44.550
and a devoted teacher.

00:00:44.550 --> 00:00:48.180
Recent Phelps lectures have
featured cultural historian

00:00:48.180 --> 00:00:51.960
