00:56:11.330 --> 00:56:13.610
My most recent
language is Icelandic.

00:56:18.828 --> 00:56:20.180
I don't know.

00:56:20.180 --> 00:56:22.760
I can't follow those
things particularly well.

00:56:22.760 --> 00:56:26.240
But I assume, since
they keep getting

00:56:26.240 --> 00:56:29.910
translated in places
like Iran and so on,

00:56:29.910 --> 00:56:34.910
that they have a reasonable
