00:56:43.780 --> 00:56:44.770
- Hi.

00:56:44.770 --> 00:56:46.690
My name is Sarah, and--

00:56:46.690 --> 00:56:48.940
oh, this is very loud.

00:56:48.940 --> 00:56:51.730
So my question is I guess
